data.description: THIS IS THE ONE! If you’ve been looking for a beautiful, commuter-friendly home in Montgomery County, you’ve found it! This gorgeous corner lot home is everything you’ve been looking for and so much more. As you drive up, you will immediately notice the beautifully landscaped yard offers so much space to enjoy the outside. Once you enter the home, you will notice fresh paint that extends from top to bottom. The spacious family room is great for relaxing. The main floor offers 2 bedrooms with a fully renovated main-level bathroom. Around the corner, you will walk into a lovely kitchen/dining room with excellent lighting, stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, custom cabinets, and a wall backsplash. Off the kitchen is a staircase that leads to the perfect basement with additional living space, offering a full bedroom and updated full bathroom, This floor is designed to entertain. Flooring throughout the home has been updated to include beautiful hardwoods, luxury vinyl, and tile. The top floor is magic, boasting an owner's suite that makes you feel royal. You notice the nicest, quaint sitting area, great for reading a book or just relaxing, with a very large master suite, and ample closet space. The full bathroom with a walk-in shower and double vanity sink is a dream. The cherry on the is that you’re on ½ mile from the DC line, downtown Silver Spring, and access to major highway 495/95. Don’t wait. This is a MUST SEE!
